[normal]Written evidence[bold] submitted by [bold]BenX[bold]BenX[bold] is a group of local authority Benefits and Revenues Services. The purpose of the group is to foster close co-operation in all fields of the administration of Housing Benefit, Council Tax Support, Council Tax and National Non Domestic Rates.  The group[bold] also has a wider role in [bold]liaising[bold] with other relevant Government agencies, including the DWP, DCLG,  Her Majesty’s Revenue &amp; Customs and Pension Service.[bold]&#xa0;
[normal]This document states the key aims and objectives of [bold]BenX[bold].  [bold]&#xa0;
[normal]&#xa0;
