[normal]Act as a discussion forum regarding new Housing Benefit/ Council Tax Support, Council Tax, NNDR (or related) legislation and policy, to assist in 
[normal]successful implementation of new procedures;
[normal]-[bold]&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0;&#xa0; 
[normal]Make recommendations and lobby for changes to Housing Benefit/ Council Tax Support, Council Tax and NNDR policy, or related areas, to improve service delivery;
